<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
      
        <%= image_tag "Profile.JPG", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">

        <p> I am driven by building highly intuitive web applications with a strong focus on user experience and beautiful design. I specialize in full stack Ruby/Rails development.  With a background in the arts and music, I also bring a keen design sensibility to all of my projects.
        </p>

        <p>I am the creator of the website AuditionCafe.com, a classical music job board that simplifies the process of finding and posting auditions. I am also the founder/director of MusAid.com, a 501(c)3 summer program that supports musical institutions around the world.
        </p>

        <p>
        I was born in Thailand and have spent the majority of my life living overseas in Vietnam, Laos, India, Kyrgyzstan and Romania.  I am currently based in beautiful Miami Beach, Florida.</p>
        


        <p>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type='button'
            data-toggle='collapse'
            data-target='#jobHistory'
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controler='jobHistory'
          >
    
          Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type='button'
            data-toggle='collapse'
            data-target='#education'
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controler='education'
          >
          
          Education
          </button>

        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jobsss
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              Jobsss
            </div>
              
          </div>

            <div class="collapse" id="education">
              <div class="card card-block">
                Yale University - MMus
              </div>

              <div class="card card-block">
                Indiana University - BMus
              </div>

              <div class="card card-block">
               <em> Courses: </em>
                <div>Learn Ruby the Hard Way - Zed A. Shaw</div>
                <div>Disecting Ruby on Rails - DevCamp</div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>       
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="https://platform.linkedin.com/badges/js/profile.js" async defer></script>


